News.Title: FLYSBS Aviation Reports Strong H1 Performance with 357% Jump in Net Profit
News.Summary: FLYSBS Aviation reported H1 net profit of 238M rupees compared to 52M rupees year-over-year, marking significant growth for the newly listed company. The aviation company's EBITDA surged to 311M rupees from 81M rupees, with EBITDA margin expanding to 22.6% from 9.7% year-over-year.
